The paper proposes a technique for domain generalization using deep neural networks and normalization layers. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of domain augmentation, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of instance normalization, which is commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL).
